Hello, 🙂 do you want to be more productive? Let's do it together! 💪 My name is Enrico, and the idea is simple: we are to do Study With Me Content for 12 hours! 60 Minutes Style! With Rain sounds, conversations during breaks, and in real-time! I am a graduate student (or a "dottore," as we say here in Italy) currently studying at Harvard University. I will take you with me on my day (live!) You guys are my Study Family ❤️, and we are here to support and motivate each other! ✨

1 ● 📆 Schedule of the Live streams - 4 Months Study Challenge

Stream Schedule: http://tinyurl.com/StreamScheduleEnrico
I am currently streaming "study with me" content every single day. I am doing the Four Months Study Challenge, which will end on May 10th (before my Summer Vacation.) The challenge is simple: Study every single day for as much time as possible! Feel free to join the challenge at any point, for four months, a few months, a couple of weeks, or whatever time you prefer; I will do this for four entire months! Take care of your health, guys, but with that being said, I am CHALLENGING myself and you, too! Do you accept this challenge? Can you study every single day? Can I do it? There is only one way to find out!

6 ● 👨‍🎓 How I Study

My study session is a 60-minute Pomodoro Timer. Then, there will be a break of 10 minutes (or 9). During the live study with me, I repeat this for 8-14 hours. This is a double Pomodoro timer (60\10 or 60\9). The Pomodoro technique is very powerful. Breaks are essential to keep the efficiency of your study high. Always take them! I have a timer for all these scenarios. 
I alway study with Discipline ( https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2uhMr4eAhQY&t=0s ) and Self-Motivation. ( https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HliXs02QPR4&t=0s )
